  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 2nd level, you learn a secret method to transform your otherwise lackluster Puppet into a force to be reckoned with.</p><p> Select one Puppet Weapon Types listed on the next page.</p><p> Your selection grants your Puppet new abilities, ability score improvements, changes its appearance, and grants it access to a Weapon Types, which lets it to transform into a weapon.</p><p> As part of rolling for initiative or as a Bonus Action, you can transform your Puppet into its Weapon Mode.</p><p> You can revert your Puppet out of this mode on your turn (no action needed).</p><p> You also gain access to Upgrades of War, which are Puppet Upgrades exclusive to the Blue Technique.</p><p></p>",
